Discord

You can get help by coming to our discord server.

Join Discord Server

How to get help?

Step 1. Join our discord server.

Join Discord Server

Step 2. Find "help-ticket" channel.

Step 3. Find this message and click on the button "Create Ticket".

Step 4. A numbered channel will be added to the ticket category, go there.

Step 5. You can state your problem here and the authorities will take care of it when they are available.

Step 6. After receiving your assistance, please close the ticket.

Need Help? Join Our Discord Server!
